@startuml delta-mixin
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class DeltaMixin <<abstract>> {
  +calculate_delta(s1, s2)
  +plot_delta(x, y) <<abstract>>
}

class MatplotlibBackend
class interpolate_series <<function>>

MatplotlibBackend --|> DeltaMixin
DeltaMixin ..> interpolate_series : uses

note right of DeltaMixin
plot_delta(...) is ABSTRACT.
Every backend that uses DeltaMixin
MUST IMPLEMENT plot_delta.

--

calculate_delta:
- interpolates s1/s2 to a common time base
- computes abs_diff
- calls plot_delta(x, abs_diff)
end note

@enduml
